trans-unit.source: Provides qualifying information to a callback method when a <see cref="E:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact.SubscribeCompleted" /> event is signaled.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona a un método de devolución de llamada información para distinguir cuándo un evento <see cref="E:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact.SubscribeCompleted" /> está señalado.

trans-unit.source: Specifies the <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact" /> for which the subscription was requested.
trans-unit.target: Especifica el objeto <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact" /> para el que se solicitó la suscripción.

trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact" /> object for which a subscription was requested.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact" /> para el que se solicitó una suscripción.

trans-unit.source: This value is `null` if the subscription is completed for an instance of <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerNearMe> that does not have an associated <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact>.
trans-unit.target: Este valor es `null` si la suscripción se ha completado para una instancia de <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerNearMe> que no tiene asociado un <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact>.

trans-unit.source: Specifies the <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerNearMe" /> for which the subscription is requested.
trans-unit.target: Especifica <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerNearMe" /> para el que se solicita la suscripción.

trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerNearMe" /> object for which a subscription was requested.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerNearMe" /> para el que se solicitó una suscripción.

trans-unit.source: This value is `null` if the subscription is requested on an instance of <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact> that does not exist in the "People Near Me" scope.
trans-unit.target: Este valor es `null` si la suscripción se solicita en una instancia de <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact> que no existe en el ámbito "People Near Me".
